Author: happybumblebree
Text: i was skinny my entire childhood. just stick thin. never cared about my weight or anything until i developed boobs. guys kept telling me that i had a big butt. i went from the nerdy freckled skinny kid to overly sexualized teenager in less than a year and that messes with someone as modest and insecure as i was.  so i did what i could to get that stick figure back and now here i am, 15 years later, disordered for good.
